        {
            "id": 5982105,
            "title": "盤中速報 - 金穎生技(1796)急拉3.66%報48.15元，成交1張",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>金穎生技(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:1796:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/1796\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">1796-TW</a>)近5分K漲速3.66%，16日09:19報48.15元，成交1張，今日漲幅為2.01％。（註：漲跌速為5分K的漲跌幅）</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>金穎生技(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:1796:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/1796\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">1796-TW</a>)近5日股價下跌1.67%。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><em>近5日籌碼</em></p></section><section><ul> <li>三大法人合計買賣超：-9 張</li> <li>外資買賣超：-8 張</li> <li>投信買賣超：0 張</li> <li>自營商買賣超：-1 張</li> <li>融資增減：+9 張</li> <li>融券增減：0 張</li> </ul></section><div class=\"dzbcd51\"></div><div class=\"m1aaic49\"></div></main>",
